World Water Week 2021 is asking for concrete examples of resilience in the face of water stress. 
Biodegradable ingredients & formulations are just one of the ways we are taking responsible action to protect and preserve water.

Another way to save the environment? Don’t poison a third world country’s indigenous community and animals with your mercury and then illegally chop more trees so you can kill them all faster. Have some shame Unilever. Disgusting
